<hymn_number>9759</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- yạ yswʿ yạ nwr yạlly ạlẓlạm ʿndk ydwb wykẖtfy

[V2]
 yạlly ạlsjyn fy mḥḍrk ynfk qydh wytʿfy

[V3]
 yạ rwḥ yạ ḥyạẗ wạlmwt dạ mạt ḥty̱ ạlmryḍ bytsẖfy

[V4]
 wạlḥzn yhrb wạlfrḥ yyjy wysẖʿ nwr mạ ynṭfy

[V5]
 1- ṣrkẖẗ ḍyạʿy wạ̉nạ lsh fy ạlạ̉kẖṭạr

[V6]
 ʿmry fy ạ̹ydyk yạ rạsm ạlmsẖwạr

[V7]
 wạ̹nt ạlly tqdr tkẖfy fyk ḍʿfy

[V8]
 bạ̹ydyk wtkẖlq gẖyr ʿmry fyk ạ̉ʿmạr

[V9]
 2- ạ̹nt ạlly mạsk bạ̹ydyk ạlạ̉yạm

[V10]
 wạ̹nt ạlly fyk ttḥqq ạlạ̉ḥlạm

[V11]
 wạ̹nt qwạya wfyk ydwb ʿjzy

[V12]
 wtbyd ẓlạmy wtmlạ qlby slạm</lyrics>
<title>yạ yswʿ yạ nwr</title>
</song>